VAV who keep improving from each album, is going to comeback with their 6th Mini Album MADE FOR TWO on coming FALL-2020.VAV 6th Mini Album MADE FOR TWO is having title song MADE FOR TWO, and also 4 track list composed by members which is ‚ÄòInto You‚Äô, ‚ÄôMoto‚Äô, ‚ÄôHold Tight‚Äô and ‚ÄôYou Taught Me Love‚Äô.MADE FOR TWO is a mid-tempo track mixing Scandinavia with North Europe style, story-telling the memories and farewell, also promise to meet again in future. The song MADE FOR TWO not only focus on past precious memories of the lovers, but also specially focus on ‚Äúpromise‚Äù and ‚Äúhope for future‚Äù.  The song is dedicate to couples, meanwhile also represent all memories and promise between VAV and VAMPZ. As for track list, first there‚Äôs ‚ÄòInto You‚Äô, a self-composed song from leader St.Van. It‚Äôs a refreshing summer EDM track with light beat. By just listening to the song, VAV seems turning back to be a teenager who is shy facing his first love. Next there‚Äôs ‚ÄòMoto‚Äô from member Ayno. It is a EDM track with strong self-personality, and it has two meanings ‚ÄùMotor‚Äù and ‚ÄùMotto‚Äù, referring that this girl is the motto of my life. We can get to know Ayno‚Äôs motto in the music industry and of course get to know more about his composing talent too.Member Ace contributed for the album with his song ‚ÄôHold Tight‚Äô. This track is a typical ballad song of VAV, talk about sadness between lovers during farewell. The song sounds heart breaking with piano sound and VAV‚Äôs beautiful voice. Lastly, we have ‚ÄôYou Taught Me Love‚Äô written by member Lou. This song was inspired by the movie A Star Is Born, fans can get to know more the affectionateness side of VAV throughout the song.VAV new song  MADE FOR TWO is about the sadness of a man during farewell, but he recalled all the beautiful memories and keep the faith for a reunion in future. Not like previous dark concept ‚ÄúPOISON‚Äù album, VAV is looking fresh and young for this up-coming new album. The MV shooting took place at Jeju Island, fans will be able to see the pretty natural scenery together with VAV dance performance and acting. This album had compiled the past 5 years of VAV, all the music and memories, also promise to meet again in future. VAV 6th Mini Album MADE FOR TWO is a precious yet meaningful album for both VAV and VAMPZ. #VAV #Î∏åÏù¥ÏóêÏù¥Î∏åÏù¥ #MADE_FOR_TWO
